  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of S-adenosyl-L-methionine in Treatment of Chronic Hepatitis B Patients With Cholestasis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of S-adenosyl-L-methionine in Treatment of Chronic Hepatitis B Patients With Cholestasis</official_title>
