  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. from 18-65 years old

          2. diagnosed as hepatitis B, previous has HBV or HBsAg(+)&gt;6 months, and now HBsAg or HBV
             DNA(+)

          3. with intrahepatic cholestasis: meet EASL 2009 diagnoses criteria ALP&gt;1.5ULN and
             GGT&gt;3ULN or STB&gt;2ULN

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. liver mass, liver carcinoma

          2. liver failure

          3. non-hepatic diseases caused jaundice

          4. obstructive jaundice
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
